name: .DACPAC File Extension
type_name: SQL Server Data Tier Application Package
summary: Learn about .DACPAC files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Data package created by a Microsoft SQL Server data tier application; contains both the schema of data as well as the data records, or objects, themselves; used for providing data between SQL Server databases and vendor applications.

content: DACPAC files use .ZIP formatting and contain a collection of XML files that define the schema and data to be transferred.
